STATE of North Carolina
v.
Jose Luis DOMINGUEZ. No. 15P16. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Jose Luis Dominguez, Lumberton, for Dominguez, Jose Luis. Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. James R. O'Neill, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 14th of January 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
JACKSON, J. recused.
